### create user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "chunkylover23",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/tokens
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "chunkylover23",
  "password": "password"
}

