### rename success
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69ab49023fc4a574c4de9d14
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cool Dog Photo"
}

### rename bad request
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69ab49023fc4a574c4de9d14
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### rename too long
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69ab49023fc4a574c4de9d14
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}

### rename not exist
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/123456789012345678901234
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Does not exist"
}